個封帳 一個唔封無事<br />\n-自慰為福地，成埋玻璃心圍爐取暖<br />\n-無pm，無派膠，彈app<br />\n-Admin幾乎完全唔更新，屈人開分身bam<br />\n「總結：比高登更垃圾的地方」<br />\n<br />\n好處<br />\n人小<br />\nSever 穩</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkgalden.com/view/392100/page/1/highlight/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkgalden.com%2Fview%2F392100%2Fpage%2F1%2Fhighlight%2F&d=vETYuIEwvbn%2BH6dyMCsmrMW%2Flfx08C7TTpsJ%2BRLLqlo%3D&h=fcb172d4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hkgalden.com/view/392100/page/1/highlight/</a><br />\n成個post都係我開嘅 唔想講啲咩<br />\n如果真係有心嘅入去睇吓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4700993aba6b02c3de5615afec374ff58d76baf2","tid":3073,"uid":1693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T05:22:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4efcb2dcff07a3bdf5637c503f1d81aa3b95403","tid":3073,"uid":12748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T05:23:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9aa191f301557eb3e7d897b11e54a3f329827472","tid":3073,"uid":1693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T05:25:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>連個app「呢加狂彈無更新」<br />\n都係lihkg搞 <br />\n難聽d講果邊只不過係拿黎小圈子打飛機既論壇</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我想講一開始嘅膠登真係唔係咁 個到好熱鬧一開始"},{"pid":"55425320be4401b98b34acbb44b3548f385a31ee","tid":3073,"uid":12748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T05:25:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ff422843a3187ff10df85b4eaee02929a3629b9d","tid":3073,"uid":83,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T05:27:04.000Z","msg":"茄寶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca2a8f8166915213c6a53f3dfc9571899891eaa4","tid":3073,"uid":1693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T05:27:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n最主要admin 管治根本已經有問題<br />\n我睇唔出作為一個管理員應有的責任<br />\n咁基本管治能力都無<br />\n呢樣林生叻過佢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我上面嗰個Post 都有講<br />\n連一個基本管理員都做唔到 只係想玩權力<br />\n唉"},{"pid":"4c45c04d6487914b937e6e86f67881a6579165a4","tid":3073,"uid":1693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T05:28:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>茄寶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果你哋歡迎我一定會一齊帶喺呢度熱潮<br />\n順便得閑分享下我嘅日常生活<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}